{"service_name": "Methods Advisory: Health Service Strategy, Planning and Change Consultancy", "service_id": "7753461044384891", "company_name": "Methods Advisory Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Methods Advisory Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Methods Advisory: Health Service Strategy, Planning and Change Consultancy\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Methods Advisory can assist and advise on all aspects of health and care service strategy, planning, change and services, including healthcare systems. We deliver advisory, delivery and assurance services across the UK. This includes central government, NHS, regulators, commissioners and providers. We can provide full lifecycle management or specialist advice.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Deep NHS Expertise, with employed care professionals and managers\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Evidence-based analysis, including international learning and comparators\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Commissioning and Procurement expertise, including clinical/ care services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Benefits/ value-led approach to planning and change\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Planning and modelling, including scenario and impact analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Change underpinned by robust business cases and strong governance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Includes organisational design and target operating models\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Emphasis on service and quality improvement, without increasing costs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Focus on pragmatic innovation, transformative but sustainable change\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Extensive stakeholder engagement experience, including patients and the public\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Low/ no learning curve, with employed care professionals and managers.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     More robust service modelling and options analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Better knowledge transfer through proven tools and processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Service improvement and change that is evidence and benefits\u2013led\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Emphasis on improving quality and safety at less cost\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Robust change methodology to manage internal governance and external scrutiny\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Better, more effective stakeholder engagement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Emphasis on measurable quality and outcome improvements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Based on leading practice change theory and techniques\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Able to draw on relevant experience across all public services\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3300 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92308/7753461044384891-pricing-document-2015-09-28-1447.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link